# Code standards (minkow.ski)

## Structure

| Concern | Location |
|---------|----------|
| Reusable UI | `src/components/ui/` |
| Feature components | `src/components/` |
| Copy and content | `src/data/` |
| Routes / paths | `src/lib/routes.ts` |
| Site config | `src/lib/site.ts` |
| Styles tokens | `src/lib/styles.ts` |
| Pure utilities | `src/lib/` |
| Route screens | `src/routes/` (orchestration only) |

## Rules

- Screens compose components; they do not define one-off layout primitives inline.
- User-facing strings live in `src/data/`, not hardcoded across multiple route files.
- Use `Card`, `LinkCard`, `PageGrid`, `ExternalLink`, and style tokens from `lib/styles.ts`.
- Route paths: `ROUTES` from `lib/routes.ts`. Site URLs: `SITE` from `lib/site.ts`.
- Class names: `cn()` from `lib/cn.ts`.
- Tests for pure logic in `src/**/*.test.ts`. Run `npm run check` before commit.

## Responsive breakpoints

| Tier | Breakpoint | Grid |
|------|------------|------|
| Mobile | default | 1 column |
| Tablet | `sm:` (640px+) | 2 columns |
| Desktop | `lg:` (1024px+) | 3 columns (home bento only) |

- Layout tokens live in `lib/layout.ts`. Page shells use `PageGrid` / `ScrollPage`.
- Home bento desktop placement uses `lg:col-start` / `lg:row-start`, not `md:`.
- Prefer `dvh` and `safe-area-inset-*` for mobile viewport and notched devices.

## Resume redirect

- App links use `/resume` only. Never put the Google Drive URL in `src/`.
- Redirect target lives in `config/resume.ts` + `public/_redirects` (prod) + Vite middleware (dev).
